CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 26, 1959, page 6, reads: "Food for the Needy - The Phalanx Club of 1960 of the Centre Ave. YMCA donated food for the needy this week. Members shown above are, left to right: Harold Blye, Charles Walker, Sydney Johnson, Nicholas Watts and Melvin Payne. Not shown are: Larry Ballow, James Cabbagestock, Edward Solomon, Robert Clayton and William Charles. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of the Phalanx Club, left to right: Harold Blye, Charles Walker, Sydney Johnson, Nicholas Watts, and Melvin Payne, standing behind table with pyramid of canned food at the Centre Avenue YMCA in the Hill District
